<https://w3id.org/earthsemantics/OSO> a owl:NamedIndividual,
        owl:Ontology ;
    rdfs:label "Οντολογία θαλάσσιων παρατηρητηρίων (OSO)"@el,
        "Observatories of the Seas Ontology (OSO)"@en,
        "Ontología de los observatorios marinos (OSO)"@es,
        "Ontologie des observatoires marins (OSO)"@fr,
        "Ontologia degli osservatori marini (OSO)"@it,
        "Ontologi for marine observatorier (OSO)"@no,
        "Ontologia dos observatórios marinhos (OSO)"@pt,
        "Ontologia observatoarelor marine (OSO)"@ro ;
    cc:license <https://creativecommons.org/licenses/by/4.0/> ;
    cc:morePermissions <https://github.com/emso-eric/oso-ontology/blob/main/LICENSE> ;
    cc:useGuidelines <https://emso-eric.github.io/oso-ontology/> ;
    omv:URI <https://w3id.org/earthsemantics/OSO> ;
    omv:acronym "OSO" ;
    omv:creationDate "2025-04-04"^^xsd:date ;
    omv:description "Οντολογία που περιγράφει τα θαλάσσια παρατηρητήρια (περιφερειακές υποδομές, τοποθεσίες, πλατφόρμες) για την υποστήριξη της διαχείρισης δεδομένων FAIR και της διαλειτουργικότητας, ιδιαίτερα στο πλαίσιο του EMSO ERIC."@el,
        "Ontology describing marine observatories (Regional Facilities, Sites, Platforms) to support FAIR data management and interoperability, particularly in the EMSO ERIC context."@en,
        "Ontología que describe los observatorios marinos (infraestructuras regionales, sitios, plataformas) para apoyar la gestión FAIR de datos y la interoperabilidad, especialmente en el contexto de EMSO ERIC."@es,
        "Ontologie décrivant les observatoires marins (infrastructures régionales, sites, plateformes) pour soutenir la gestion FAIR des données et l’interopérabilité, notamment dans le cadre d’EMSO ERIC."@fr,
        "Ontologia che descrive gli osservatori marini (infrastrutture regionali, siti, piattaforme) per supportare la gestione FAIR dei dati e l’interoperabilità, in particolare nel contesto EMSO ERIC."@it,
        "Ontologi som beskriver marine observatorier (regionale fasiliteter, steder, plattformer) for å støtte FAIR datastyring og interoperabilitet, spesielt i EMSO ERIC-konteksten."@no,
        "Ontologia que descreve os observatórios marinhos (infraestruturas regionais, locais, plataformas) para apoiar a gestão FAIR de dados e a interoperabilidade, especialmente no contexto do EMSO ERIC."@pt,
        "Ontologia care descrie observatoarele marine (facilități regionale, situri, platforme) pentru a susține gestionarea FAIR a datelor și interoperabilitatea, în special în contextul EMSO ERIC."@ro ;
    omv:designedForOntologyTask omv:AnnotationTask,
        omv:IndexingTask,
        omv:IntegrationTask,
        omv:QueryFormulationTask ;
    omv:documentation <https://emso-eric.github.io/oso-ontology/>,
        <https://github.com/emso-eric/oso-ontology> ;
    omv:endorsedBy OSO:EMSO_DMSG ;
    omv:hasDomain <https://data.earthportal.eu/categories/CLIMATE>,
        <https://data.earthportal.eu/categories/EARTH>,
        <https://data.earthportal.eu/categories/ENV>,
        "Θαλάσσιες ερευνητικές υποδομές"@el,
        "Marine Research Infrastructures"@en,
        "Infraestructuras de investigación marina"@es,
        "Infrastructures de recherche marine"@fr,
        "Infrastrutture di ricerca marina"@it,
        "Marine forskningsinfrastrukturer"@no,
        "Infraestruturas de investigação marinha"@pt,
        "Infrastructuri de cercetare marină"@ro ;
    omv:hasFormalityLevel <http://w3id.org/nkos/nkostype#ontology> ;
    omv:hasOntologyLanguage "OWL" ;
    omv:hasOntologyName "Οντολογία των θαλάσσιων παρατηρητηρίων (OSO)"@el,
        "Observatories of the Seas Ontology (OSO)"@en,
        "Ontología de los observatorios marinos (OSO)"@es,
        "Ontologie des observatoires marins (OSO)"@fr,
        "Ontologia degli osservatori marini (OSO)"@it,
        "Ontologi for marine observatorier (OSO)"@no,
        "Ontologia dos observatórios marinhos (OSO)"@pt,
        "Ontologia observatoarelor marine (OSO)"@ro ;
    omv:hasOntologySyntax <http://www.w3.org/ns/formats/Turtle> ;
    omv:hasOntologyType "Application ontology" ;
    omv:keywords "θαλάσσια παρατηρητήρια, δεδομένα FAIR, EMSO, ερευνητικές υποδομές, οντολογία, υποβρύχια παρατηρητήρια"@el,
        "marine observatories, FAIR data, EMSO, research infrastructures, ontology, underwater observatories"@en,
        "observatorios marinos, datos FAIR, EMSO, infraestructuras de investigación, ontología, observatorios submarinos"@es,
        "observatoires marins, données FAIR, EMSO, infrastructures de recherche, ontologie, observatoires sous-marins"@fr,
        "osservatori marini, dati FAIR, EMSO, infrastrutture di ricerca, ontologia, osservatori sottomarini"@it,
        "marine observatorier, FAIR-data, EMSO, forskningsinfrastrukturer, ontologi, undervannsobservatorier"@no,
        "observatórios marinhos, dados FAIR, EMSO, infraestruturas de investigação, ontologia, observatórios subaquáticos"@pt,
        "observatoare marine, date FAIR, EMSO, infrastructuri de cercetare, ontologie, observatoare subacvatice"@ro ;
    omv:name "Οντολογία θαλάσσιων παρατηρητηρίων"@el,
        "Observatories of the Seas Ontology"@en,
        "Ontología de los observatorios marinos"@es,
        "Ontologie des observatoires marins"@fr,
        "Ontologia degli osservatori marini"@it,
        "Ontologi for marine observatorier"@no,
        "Ontologia dos observatórios marinhos"@pt,
        "Ontologia observatoarelor marine"@ro ;
    omv:naturalLanguage "el",
        "en",
        "es",
        "fr",
        "it",
        "no",
        "pt",
        "ro" ;
    omv:numberOfAxioms 17934 ;
    omv:numberOfClasses 60 ;
    omv:numberOfIndividuals 575 ;
    omv:numberOfProperties 175 ;
    omv:ontologyPurpose "Περιγραφή της δομής και των βασικών στοιχείων των θαλάσσιων παρατηρητηρίων για τη βελτίωση της διαχείρισης δεδομένων, της διαλειτουργικότητας και της επαναχρησιμοποίησης, ιδιαίτερα στο πλαίσιο της υποδομής EMSO."@el,
        "Describe the structure and key components of marine observatories to improve data management, interoperability, and reuse, especially in the EMSO research infrastructure context."@en,
        "Describir la estructura y los componentes clave de los observatorios marinos para mejorar la gestión de datos, la interoperabilidad y la reutilización, especialmente en el contexto de la infraestructura de investigación EMSO."@es,
        "Décrire la structure et les composants clés des observatoires marins afin d'améliorer la gestion, l'interopérabilité et la réutilisation des données, notamment dans le cadre de l'infrastructure de recherche EMSO."@fr,
        "Descrivere la struttura e i principali componenti degli osservatori marini per migliorare la gestione, l'interoperabilità e il riutilizzo dei dati, in particolare nel contesto dell'infrastruttura di ricerca EMSO."@it,
        "Beskrive strukturen og hovedkomponentene i marine observatorier for å forbedre datastyring, interoperabilitet og gjenbruk, spesielt i EMSO-forskningsinfrastrukturens kontekst."@no,
        "Descrever a estrutura e os principais componentes dos observatórios marinhos para melhorar a gestão de dados, a interoperabilidade e a reutilização, especialmente no contexto da infraestrutura de investigação EMSO."@pt,
        "Descrierea structurii și a componentelor cheie ale observatoarelor marine pentru a îmbunătăți gestionarea, interoperabilitatea și reutilizarea datelor, în special în contextul infrastructurii EMSO."@ro ;
    omv:reference <https://doi.org/10.25504/FAIRsharing.654931>,
        <https://doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.19497913>,
        <https://earthportal.eu/ontologies/OSO>,
        <https://github.com/emso-eric/oso-ontology>,
        <https://www.emso-fr.org/Data/Observatories-of-Seas-Ontology> ;
    omv:resourceLocator <https://w3id.org/earthsemantics/OSO> ;
    omv:status "Published" ;
    omv:useImports rdfs:,
        owl:,
        skos:,
        foaf: ;
    omv:usedOntologyEngineeringMethodology <https://w3id.org/okn/o/sd#OntologyEngineering> ;
    omv:usedOntologyEngineeringTool "Protégé 5.6.9",
        "VSCodium 1.92.2" ;
    omv:version "1.0.5" ;
    dcterms:abstract "Η οντολογία OSO οργανώνει τα θαλάσσια παρατηρητήρια σε τρία ιεραρχικά επίπεδα: περιφερειακές υποδομές, τοποθεσίες και πλατφόρμες. Υποστηρίζει τη διαχείριση δεδομένων σύμφωνα με τις αρχές FAIR, τη διαλειτουργικότητα και την ενσωμάτωση πληροφοριών για θαλάσσιες υποδομές, ιδιαίτερα στο πλαίσιο του EMSO ERIC."@el,
        "The OSO ontology structures marine observatories into three hierarchical levels: Regional Facilities, Sites, and Platforms. It supports FAIR data management, interoperability, and integration of heterogeneous marine infrastructure information, particularly within the EMSO ERIC framework."@en,
        "La ontología OSO estructura los observatorios marinos en tres niveles jerárquicos: infraestructuras regionales, sitios y plataformas. Apoya la gestión FAIR de datos, la interoperabilidad y la integración de información sobre infraestructuras marinas, especialmente en el contexto de EMSO ERIC."@es,
        "L'ontologie OSO structure les observatoires marins en trois niveaux hiérarchiques : infrastructures régionales, sites et plateformes. Elle soutient la gestion FAIR des données, l'interopérabilité et l'intégration des informations sur les infrastructures marines, notamment dans le cadre d'EMSO ERIC."@fr,
        "L'ontologia OSO struttura gli osservatori marini in tre livelli gerarchici: infrastrutture regionali, siti e piattaforme. Supporta la gestione FAIR dei dati, l'interoperabilità e l'integrazione delle informazioni sulle infrastrutture marine, in particolare nel contesto EMSO ERIC."@it,
        "OSO-ontologien strukturerer marine observatorier i tre hierarkiske nivåer: regionale fasiliteter, steder og plattformer. Den støtter FAIR datastyring, interoperabilitet og integrasjon av informasjon om marine infrastrukturer, spesielt i EMSO ERIC-konteksten."@no,
        "A ontologia OSO estrutura os observatórios marinhos em três níveis hierárquicos: infraestruturas regionais, locais e plataformas. Suporta a gestão FAIR de dados, a interoperabilidade e a integração de informações sobre infraestruturas marinhas, especialmente no contexto do EMSO ERIC."@pt,
        "Ontologia OSO structurează observatoarele marine în trei niveluri ierarhice: facilități regionale, situri și platforme. Susține gestionarea FAIR a datelor, interoperabilitatea și integrarea informațiilor despre infrastructuri marine, în special în contextul EMSO ERIC."@ro ;
    dcterms:bibliographicCitation "Observatories of the Seas Ontology (OSO), version 1.0.5 EMSO ERIC / Ifremer. FAIRsharing DOI: 10.25504/FAIRsharing.654931."@en ;
