        "Ontologi for marine observatorier"@no,
        "Ontologia dos observatórios marinhos"@pt,
        "Ontologia observatoarelor marine"@ro ;
    skos:scopeNote "Να μην συγχέεται με το OpenScienceOntology (OSO) ή το Ontology for Scenario Orchestration (OSO)."@el,
        "Not to be confused with OpenScienceOntology (OSO) or Ontology for Scenario Orchestration (OSO)."@en,
        "No confundir con OpenScienceOntology (OSO) ni con Ontology for Scenario Orchestration (OSO)."@es,
        "À ne pas confondre avec OpenScienceOntology (OSO) ni avec Ontology for Scenario Orchestration (OSO)."@fr,
        "Da non confondere con OpenScienceOntology (OSO) o Ontology for Scenario Orchestration (OSO)."@it,
        "Må ikke forveksles med OpenScienceOntology (OSO) eller Ontology for Scenario Orchestration (OSO)."@no,
        "Não confundir com OpenScienceOntology (OSO) nem com Ontology for Scenario Orchestration (OSO)."@pt,
        "A nu se confunda cu OpenScienceOntology (OSO) sau cu Ontology for Scenario Orchestration (OSO)."@ro ;
